Template: ola/daemon
Type: boolean
Default: false
_Description: Should the ola daemon be started at boot?
 The ola daemon is needed to use ola.
 .
 You have the option of starting the ola daemon automatically on
 system boot. If in doubt, it is suggested to not start it
 automatically on boot.
 .
 This setting can be modified later by running 'dpkg-reconfigure ola'.
